text: This section describes the Categorized Grouping profile and agent. The agent is a processing agent for batch workflow configurations. Prerequisites The reader of this information has to be familiar with: Analysis Programming Language UDR structure and contents User Documentation The Analysis Programming Language description and syntax are listed in the APL Reference Guide . The Ultra Format Definition La ngu age is described in the Ultra Reference Guide .
